g3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Th%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Thi%C3%AAn-h%E1%BA%A1-h%C6%B0ng-vong-tr%E1%BB%8B-lo%E1%BA%A1n-chi-nguy%C3%AAn-lu%E1%BA%ADn/poem-B5-ZRUV5hM7ePrPE55xABA">Thiên hạ hưng vong trị loạn chi nguyên luận - 天下興亡治亂之原論</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Th%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-RAeWvfd20Ow36nElVeRlSw">Viên Thông thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-kinh-ph%C3%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ti%C3%AAn-huy%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-qHlDll4qtUH2nCJy2-kR4Q">Tự kinh phó Phụng Tiên huyện vịnh hoài ngũ bách tự - 自京赴奉先縣詠懷五百字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%B9ng/poem-gGXMjqTTUrdwriPEB0cMQw">Tứ tùng - 四松</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
